{"tid":1201250,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"［宣傳post］《燈靈》已出書 - 612 政總外 簽名+取書 有無人嚟？","createTime":"2019-06-11T03:35:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T10:20:55.000Z","uid":90710,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7070c91608bcee9126e2bd98dc4fabaa09673740","tid":1201250,"uid":90710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T03:35:29.000Z","msg":"無文出，而又開post 宣傳新書，本身都覺得有啲心虛。（新故事其實寫緊架喇，再等下）<br />\n<br />\n畢竟《燈靈》呢個故事屬於舊登年代，唔知道呢度有幾多讀者係因為以前睇過呢個故事而認識我。<br />\n<br />\n關於實體書，大家可以點入出版社條link 望下，順手俾個like：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/169705509773757/posts/2292647900812830?s=513297068&amp;sfns=xmo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F169705509773757%2Fposts%2F2292647900812830%3Fs%3D513297068%26sfns%3Dxmo&d=0xAgwAOhMzbM3o1MPcLVD4HZfmY0V3SDPlGVafywHRI%3D&h=436d0c07\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/169705509773757/posts/2292647900812830?s=513297068&amp;sfns=xmo</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n順帶一提，其實早前嘅《我還是救護員的日子》都係由小弟所寫，只不過當時用咗另一個名出post。救護故嘅實體書亦於各大書店有售，在此要多謝已經買咗書/睇過呢個故事嘅朋友。<br />\n<br />\n然後我終於開咗 facebook page 喇，只要search 「八運當令」 就會搵到，大家可以入去like 下！<br />\n<br />\n想睇返我舊時嘅故事，可以去紙言：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.shikoto.com/search.html?query=%E5%85%AB%E9%81%8B%E7%95%B6%E4%BB%A4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.shikoto.com%2Fsearch.html%3Fquery%3D%25E5%2585%25AB%25E9%2581%258B%25E7%2595%25B6%25E4%25BB%25A4&d=0xAgwAOhMzbM3o1MPcLVD4HZfmY0V3SDPlGVafywHRI%3D&h=8327f3e3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.shikoto.com/search.html?query=%E5%85%AB%E9%81%8B%E7%95%B6%E4%BB%A4</a><br />\n<br />\n老套嘢唔講咁多，醉翁之意不在酒。<br />\n<br />\n就咁嘅，話說我手頭上仲有幾本燈靈喺手，唔知有無讀者有興趣？（特別贈送 + 簽名）<br />\n<br />\n聽日我會喺政總外面睇下書同寫下故咁，有興趣取書/簽名嘅朋友喺facebook度pm 我，約個時間到時見！<br />\n<br />\n雖然我都知自己無乜影響力，或者到最後係完全無人理我......但咩都試下，唔好咩？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<em>「於自己的能力範圍之內，能做到多少，便做多少，趁自己頭上那盞靈燈還未熄滅掉之前。」-《燈靈》</em><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n感謝支持。"},{"pid":"deaa00f259ac22e38a69bee439d5e360575286bc","tid":1201250,"uid":15395,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T03:36:48.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc8f045f8a9c50dd43f8ea13cd2238db85c6e6c3","tid":1201250,"uid":90710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"deaa00f259ac22e38a69bee439d5e360575286bc","tid":1201250,"uid":15395,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T03:36:48.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T03:52:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6381c296e77e727d75e572924234e970333a20d8","tid":1201250,"uid":176368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T06:19:32.000Z","msg":"有冇修訂過內容"},{"pid":"a9f3a782d367de8bc2c4e7d8719ae3fb97bb8238","tid":1201250,"uid":48579,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T06:20:49.000Z","msg":"想做香蕉奶？"},{"pid":"97272e8bbb570eb3f5151feb64045f415e7f6ec6","tid":1201250,"uid":90710,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6381c296e77e727d75e572924234e970333a20d8","tid":1201250,"uid":176368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T06:19:32.000Z","msg":"有冇修訂過內容"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T06:45:34.000Z","msg":"有個屬於 阿飛嘅外傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd3d76272b8d8079070e953b9efdfac7c044758c","tid":1201250,"uid":90710,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a9f3a782d367de8bc2c4e7d8719ae3fb97bb8238","tid":1201250,"uid":48579,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T06:20:49.000Z","msg":"想做香蕉奶？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T06:49:02.000Z","msg":"恕我孤陋寡聞，咩嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"134ceb6fc5ce21c829811ccbf70c577c7b3c68a1","tid":1201250,"uid":38861,"